post.title: Web.SkinUI Project
post.content: Since the MSDN magazine is “on the streets”, I’ve added a project page for the Web.SkinUI project. It will be a place for me to post updates and errata. I’ve already got a couple of things on my to do list, and I’m open to more suggestions.
